59:34.018 --> 59:36.018
He"s been our neighbour
since before you were born.

59:36.042 --> 59:38.620
Dad, every serial killer
is somebody"s neighbour-

59:38.644 --> 59:39.966
That milk carton.

59:39.990 --> 59:43.590
That t-shit and
the storage unit?

59:43.614 --> 59:45.730
That-that doesn"t
prove anything, guys.

59:45.754 --> 59:47.234
How could you guys
go along with this?

59:47.258 --> 59:49.458
We wouldn"t have if it
didn't make so much sense.

59:49.482 --> 59:51.122
