Jesus, you have
been spying on him?

59:52.692 --> 59:54.187
Yeah, we had to!

59:54.211 --> 59:57.086
And the more we watched, the
more the details stack up.

59:57.110 --> 59:58.950
He goes jogging at
11:00 at night.

