Oh.

01:01:56.954 --> 01:02:00.244
Well.

01:02:00.268 --> 01:02:01.486
Uh...

01:02:07.137 --> 01:02:09.736
I"m sorry, it's just the
uh, guys at the station

01:02:09.760 --> 01:02:12.325
